1
00:00:30,220 --> 00:00:31,980
Mr. Gu,

2
00:00:32,500 --> 00:00:36,019
since your identity was made public,

3
00:00:36,020 --> 00:00:40,099
the image of both you and the company
has been moving in a positive direction.

4
00:00:40,100 --> 00:00:42,739
We all watched your interview
with Ms. Xu.

5
00:00:42,740 --> 00:00:44,619
It was excellent.

6
00:00:44,620 --> 00:00:48,180
(Video Conference in Progress)
You're now the dream lover in everyone's heart.

7
00:00:50,780 --> 00:00:52,020
I'm married.

8
00:01:28,700 --> 00:01:29,820
Shen Gu.

9
00:02:15,140 --> 00:02:16,260
Wanxin...

10
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:23,730
♪A lonely bench on the street corner♪

11
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:28,070
♪Where all feelings come to rest♪

12
00:02:29,550 --> 00:02:33,820
♪In the night sky, the moon's trail♪

13
00:02:33,980 --> 00:02:37,579
♪Stitches up and soothes my sorrow♪

14
00:02:37,580 --> 00:02:40,549
♪The courage to get close to you♪

15
00:02:40,550 --> 00:02:44,440
♪Drives away my hesitation♪

16
00:02:44,910 --> 00:02:47,119
♪Fate turns and brings us together♪

17
00:02:47,120 --> 00:02:49,139
♪I search my memories with all my might♪

18
00:02:49,140 --> 00:02:51,840
♪Love catches me off guard♪

19
00:02:52,110 --> 00:02:54,169
♪You, in the album♪

20
00:02:54,170 --> 00:02:59,039
♪Shine through my past like starlight♪

21
00:02:59,040 --> 00:03:02,200
=Echoes of Gang City=

22
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:08,000
=Episode 21=
(Shen Gu's Long Journey Through Hardship)

23
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,500
Mr. Shen,

24
00:03:15,020 --> 00:03:16,780
why didn't you tell me
you had to work tonight?

25
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:18,840
(Video Conference in Progress)

26
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:33,060
Let me introduce.

27
00:03:33,140 --> 00:03:35,339
Chief anchor of Gang City Finance

28
00:03:35,340 --> 00:03:36,900
and Chairwoman of Minghui Group.

29
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,980
My wife, Xu Wanxin.

30
00:03:42,180 --> 00:03:43,300
Hello.

31
00:03:43,740 --> 00:03:45,060
I'm Xu Wanxin.

32
00:03:45,580 --> 00:03:49,299
Your financial interview
was as professional

33
00:03:49,300 --> 00:03:50,660
and insightful as ever.

34
00:03:50,780 --> 00:03:53,459
She'll also be more involved
in our decision-making going forward.

35
00:03:53,460 --> 00:03:56,340
I hope you'll support her
just as you support me.

36
00:03:58,060 --> 00:03:58,779
Of course.

37
00:03:58,780 --> 00:04:00,020
We'll give her our full support.

38
00:04:00,340 --> 00:04:01,380
Thank you.

39
00:04:01,540 --> 00:04:04,580
I'll be counting on you all.

40
00:04:05,020 --> 00:04:06,219
That's it for today's meeting.

41
00:04:06,220 --> 00:04:07,259
See you next time.

42
00:04:07,260 --> 00:04:08,339
See you.

43
00:04:08,340 --> 00:04:09,340
Bye.

44
00:04:14,620 --> 00:04:16,260
Why didn't you tell me
you had a meeting?

45
00:04:17,980 --> 00:04:19,139
There's a time difference.

46
00:04:19,140 --> 00:04:21,540
I was going to head back after it ended.

47
00:04:21,940 --> 00:04:23,860
There were so many of them just now.

48
00:04:24,340 --> 00:04:25,460
I...

49
00:04:26,760 --> 00:04:28,939
You're my top decision-maker.

50
00:04:28,940 --> 00:04:30,060
That's fine.

51
00:04:43,940 --> 00:04:45,380
Let's head back.

52
00:05:01,740 --> 00:05:04,700
Why is this photo here?

53
00:05:05,660 --> 00:05:07,259
It's a gift from you.

54
00:05:07,260 --> 00:05:08,660
I did?

55
00:05:09,220 --> 00:05:10,540
I don't remember.

56
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:15,739
When Qingniao was starting to pick up,

57
00:05:15,740 --> 00:05:17,780
I wanted you to be the first to know.

58
00:05:18,260 --> 00:05:20,060
So I came back to Gang City,

59
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:21,659
dressed up as a teddy bear,

60
00:05:21,660 --> 00:05:23,340
and snuck into your school.

61
00:05:24,660 --> 00:05:28,380
We graduated!

62
00:05:29,220 --> 00:05:30,860
Xu Wanxin.

63
00:05:31,620 --> 00:05:33,059
I'll make you

64
00:05:33,060 --> 00:05:36,659
the most popular financial anchor
in Gang City.

65
00:05:36,660 --> 00:05:39,259
Then I'll make you

66
00:05:39,260 --> 00:05:42,139
the youngest top producer
in the station.

67
00:05:42,140 --> 00:05:43,539
Let's take over the entire

68
00:05:43,540 --> 00:05:46,379
Gang City media industry together!

69
00:05:46,380 --> 00:05:47,219
The future looks bright.

70
00:05:47,220 --> 00:05:48,260
The future looks bright.

71
00:05:49,060 --> 00:05:50,140
Good.

72
00:05:50,580 --> 00:05:51,379
Mr. Xu, you're here.

73
00:05:51,380 --> 00:05:52,539
Grandfather.

74
00:05:52,540 --> 00:05:54,100
You've got big ambitions.

75
00:05:55,940 --> 00:05:57,979
That's wonderful. You're here.

76
00:05:57,980 --> 00:05:59,459
My dear daughter

77
00:05:59,460 --> 00:06:02,060
is going to become the lead anchor
of a financial program.

78
00:06:02,140 --> 00:06:03,859
I'm proud of you.

79
00:06:03,860 --> 00:06:06,179
Dad, you'd better work hard

80
00:06:06,180 --> 00:06:09,820
and try to become a guest on my show.

81
00:06:24,980 --> 00:06:27,260
Wait. The teddy bear is so cute.

82
00:06:27,340 --> 00:06:28,740
I want to take a photo with the bear.

83
00:06:29,140 --> 00:06:30,460
Excuse me.

84
00:06:33,140 --> 00:06:34,819
Can we take a picture together?

85
00:06:34,820 --> 00:06:35,860
Me?

86
00:06:40,420 --> 00:06:41,740
Hi, little bear.

87
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,380
Look here.

88
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:46,139
Let's say "Happy Graduation!"

89
00:06:46,140 --> 00:06:48,900
Happy Graduation!

90
00:06:51,820 --> 00:06:53,340
Thank you so much.

91
00:06:53,820 --> 00:06:55,100
Thank you.

92
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:57,460
Happy graduation.

93
00:06:57,860 --> 00:06:58,980
Wishing you a bright future.

94
00:06:59,500 --> 00:07:00,340
Mm.

95
00:07:00,400 --> 00:07:06,150
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

96
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:13,159
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

97
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:16,260
♪The promise we made♪

98
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:19,340
There, there.

99
00:07:21,940 --> 00:07:22,860
Stop crying.

100
00:07:25,820 --> 00:07:26,940
Shen Gu,

101
00:07:28,900 --> 00:07:31,540
what else do I not know about you?

102
00:07:35,340 --> 00:07:36,579
Come with me.

103
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:39,469
♪I've always been behind you♪

104
00:07:39,470 --> 00:07:44,720
♪As long as you're here, I have it all♪

105
00:07:44,900 --> 00:07:48,780
♪The whole universe♪

106
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:07,860
These are my favorite comic books.

107
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:15,660
I've prepared so many gifts for you
all these years.

108
00:08:16,220 --> 00:08:18,700
I didn't know if I'd ever
get the chance to give them to you.

109
00:08:28,380 --> 00:08:29,500
This

110
00:08:30,580 --> 00:08:32,740
is the teddy bear from the year
I was born?

111
00:08:46,140 --> 00:08:47,260
Nothing inside.

112
00:08:49,420 --> 00:08:50,540
This was what held it.

113
00:09:09,780 --> 00:09:10,940
What's this?

114
00:09:13,020 --> 00:09:16,300
A compilation of your
on-air slip-ups over the years.

115
00:09:18,940 --> 00:09:19,939
All of them.

116
00:09:19,940 --> 00:09:21,060
Don't look.

117
00:09:21,220 --> 00:09:22,219
This too.

118
00:09:22,220 --> 00:09:23,340
Give it back.

119
00:10:08,880 --> 00:10:12,160
(Trending Topic: Shen Gu
Talks About His Startup Story)

120
00:10:26,580 --> 00:10:28,379
He's a criminal's son.
What's there to talk about?

121
00:10:28,380 --> 00:10:28,979
Exactly.

122
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:29,699
Disgusting.

123
00:10:29,700 --> 00:10:30,829
Tell me about it.

124
00:10:30,830 --> 00:10:31,719
If you don't know the full story,

125
00:10:31,720 --> 00:10:32,919
don't talk nonsense.

126
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:34,379
Their family is the real victim.

127
00:10:34,380 --> 00:10:36,180
Stop spreading rumors.

128
00:11:33,180 --> 00:11:35,460
I'll have Xi handle that.

129
00:11:36,540 --> 00:11:38,460
Once this settles down,

130
00:11:40,940 --> 00:11:42,580
we'll go visit Mom together,

131
00:11:43,420 --> 00:11:44,540
alright?

132
00:11:45,340 --> 00:11:46,460
Alright.

133
00:11:48,460 --> 00:11:50,060
Go freshen up.

134
00:11:50,460 --> 00:11:51,780
I'll drive you to work.

135
00:11:53,220 --> 00:11:54,900
I'm off today.

136
00:12:04,260 --> 00:12:05,260
What's wrong?

137
00:12:09,940 --> 00:12:10,940
What's it?

138
00:12:19,140 --> 00:12:20,260
It's fine.

139
00:12:22,260 --> 00:12:23,059
Don't move.

140
00:12:23,060 --> 00:12:24,260
Don't smudge it.

141
00:12:28,260 --> 00:12:29,020
What are you doing?

142
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:31,660
Trying to cover up the evidence?

143
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:34,780
It won't look good if someone sees this.

144
00:12:36,380 --> 00:12:37,220
Stop it.

145
00:12:37,460 --> 00:12:38,419
Go to work now.

146
00:12:38,420 --> 00:12:39,580
Give me a kiss.

147
00:12:40,380 --> 00:12:41,500
Go.

148
00:12:41,580 --> 00:12:42,259
Give me a kiss.

149
00:12:42,260 --> 00:12:42,899
Go to work now.

150
00:12:42,900 --> 00:12:43,980
Give me a kiss.

151
00:12:44,220 --> 00:12:45,339
Go

152
00:12:45,340 --> 00:12:46,460
to work.

153
00:12:47,100 --> 00:12:48,180
Just one kiss.

154
00:13:00,540 --> 00:13:01,260
Boss,

155
00:13:01,420 --> 00:13:03,339
Yinghai Group has just made
an announcement without informing us.

156
00:13:03,340 --> 00:13:05,659
Due to unforeseen compliance reviews,

157
00:13:05,660 --> 00:13:06,419
they'll suspend

158
00:13:06,420 --> 00:13:09,059
all high-performance computing equipment

159
00:13:09,060 --> 00:13:10,540
and technical support indefinitely
to Qingniao.

160
00:13:14,660 --> 00:13:15,779
Have you told Fang Hongsheng?

161
00:13:15,780 --> 00:13:17,260
Lawyer Fang is already inside.

162
00:13:21,440 --> 00:13:22,739
(Video Conference in Progress)

163
00:13:22,740 --> 00:13:23,860
I understand.

164
00:13:23,940 --> 00:13:26,219
My father boarded a flight
three hours ago.

165
00:13:26,220 --> 00:13:28,260
He's working on it.

166
00:13:40,580 --> 00:13:41,980
How long can we hold out?

167
00:13:42,140 --> 00:13:45,260
I've told the team to push
legal procedures as fast as possible.

168
00:13:45,340 --> 00:13:46,860
Even if my dad steps in,

169
00:13:47,220 --> 00:13:49,260
cross-border cases will take
at least three months.

170
00:13:52,340 --> 00:13:53,460
What about you?

171
00:13:54,130 --> 00:13:56,459
Yinghai Group's suspension
takes effect immediately.

172
00:13:56,460 --> 00:13:58,579
Even with all energy-saving
and task-scheduling optimization measures

173
00:13:58,580 --> 00:14:00,579
applied to our current inventory,

174
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:02,139
we can only guarantee the operation
of the Spark core risk control module

175
00:14:02,140 --> 00:14:03,899
and the two highest-priority
research projects.

176
00:14:03,900 --> 00:14:06,139
All the other newly signed projects

177
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:08,739
will only be able to sustain low-precision
computing for 72 hours at most.

178
00:14:08,740 --> 00:14:09,979
Have we started backup plans?

179
00:14:09,980 --> 00:14:11,459
We've reached out

180
00:14:11,460 --> 00:14:13,700
to other global suppliers,

181
00:14:13,740 --> 00:14:15,739
including Yinghai's secondary channels.

182
00:14:15,740 --> 00:14:17,859
But they're all under pressure

183
00:14:17,860 --> 00:14:20,219
from Yinghai and its affiliates.

184
00:14:20,220 --> 00:14:22,539
They've made it clear.
They won't supply us.

185
00:14:22,540 --> 00:14:25,339
Even if we find a new supplier,

186
00:14:25,340 --> 00:14:27,259
we all know there's a huge generational
gap in terms of computing density,

187
00:14:27,260 --> 00:14:28,659
software ecosystem compatibility,

188
00:14:28,660 --> 00:14:29,899
and especially for the specific AI

189
00:14:29,900 --> 00:14:32,060
training and inference cores we require.

190
00:14:32,540 --> 00:14:35,099
They can't meet Spark's scale and
precision requirements in the short term.

191
00:14:35,100 --> 00:14:36,579
Also, Raymond Group has teamed up

192
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:38,539
with nine of our competitors

193
00:14:38,540 --> 00:14:40,660
to pressure Yinghai Group.

194
00:14:41,620 --> 00:14:43,739
In the end, they chose to cut us off.

195
00:14:43,740 --> 00:14:45,539
They're using Yinghai Group

196
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:46,539
to impose technological dominance
on us

197
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:48,100
through unfair competition.

198
00:14:53,781 --> 00:14:56,541
Guys, this is our test.

199
00:14:56,940 --> 00:14:59,539
Activate all contingency plans.

200
00:14:59,540 --> 00:15:01,860
Focus computing power
on solving supply issues.

201
00:15:02,740 --> 00:15:03,860
This won't be easy for us.

202
00:15:15,340 --> 00:15:16,380
You're back.

203
00:15:19,770 --> 00:15:21,140
Why are you cooking for yourself?

204
00:15:22,620 --> 00:15:24,180
I wanted to make you some soup.

205
00:15:24,820 --> 00:15:26,700
Here, try it.

206
00:15:30,460 --> 00:15:31,580
How is it?

207
00:15:32,380 --> 00:15:33,500
It's good.

208
00:15:39,980 --> 00:15:41,140
But

209
00:15:41,460 --> 00:15:44,300
I can't stay home for dinner tonight.

210
00:15:44,500 --> 00:15:46,180
I need to go to Shen City right away.

211
00:15:54,380 --> 00:15:56,060
Did something happen at the company?

212
00:16:12,820 --> 00:16:16,260
Yinghai Group is suspending supply

213
00:16:16,420 --> 00:16:18,019
to Qingniao indefinitely

214
00:16:18,020 --> 00:16:19,700
due to unforeseen compliance reviews.

215
00:16:20,420 --> 00:16:22,940
Yinghai is your biggest supplier.

216
00:16:23,180 --> 00:16:24,580
If they cut you off,

217
00:16:26,460 --> 00:16:28,340
your system could collapse.

218
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:32,940
It can get tricky.

219
00:16:33,340 --> 00:16:35,419
That's why I need to head back
to the headquarters

220
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:37,660
and coordinate with the tech team.

221
00:16:46,540 --> 00:16:47,660
When I get back,

222
00:16:47,780 --> 00:16:49,379
you can make me soup again,

223
00:16:49,380 --> 00:16:50,580
alright?

224
00:16:50,980 --> 00:16:52,900
You can have the soup anytime you want.

225
00:16:53,660 --> 00:16:55,380
The company comes first right now.

226
00:17:01,340 --> 00:17:02,460
How long

227
00:17:03,420 --> 00:17:04,740
will you be gone?

228
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:06,940
I'm not sure yet.

229
00:17:07,340 --> 00:17:08,900
But I'll be back as soon as I can.

230
00:17:13,140 --> 00:17:14,460
For now,

231
00:17:14,940 --> 00:17:17,700
I'll be fully focused on the company.

232
00:17:18,740 --> 00:17:20,460
I might not have much time for you.

233
00:17:21,380 --> 00:17:22,859
Maybe you could move back

234
00:17:22,860 --> 00:17:24,460
and stay with Grandfather for a while.

235
00:17:26,540 --> 00:17:27,940
Don't worry.

236
00:17:28,260 --> 00:17:30,460
I'll take care of myself.

237
00:17:33,740 --> 00:17:35,860
Just focus on the company.

238
00:17:38,860 --> 00:17:40,460
No matter what happens,

239
00:17:41,940 --> 00:17:43,460
Minghui and I

240
00:17:44,460 --> 00:17:46,260
will always have your back.

241
00:18:30,580 --> 00:18:36,380
♪Tonight the rain falls soft and slow♪

242
00:18:37,660 --> 00:18:43,460
♪Blending with letters left unread
drifting through the air♪

243
00:18:44,180 --> 00:18:49,540
♪You turn and look back at me♪

244
00:18:50,660 --> 00:18:56,180
♪In those same eyes familiar tears
quietly appear♪

245
00:18:57,020 --> 00:19:02,660
♪It feels like we have carried so much♪

246
00:19:03,940 --> 00:19:09,420
♪So many questions time itself
could not make clear♪

247
00:19:10,540 --> 00:19:15,860
♪The moment you walked into my life♪

248
00:19:17,020 --> 00:19:22,820
♪Every dream I had became something
I want with you near♪

249
00:19:23,220 --> 00:19:30,180
♪How many letters have I written
just for you?♪

250
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:35,980
♪If only you could truly hear
what my heart is trying to say♪

251
00:19:36,660 --> 00:19:43,019
♪From this life on
no distance could keep us apart♪

252
00:19:43,020 --> 00:19:45,899
♪The promise we made♪

253
00:19:45,900 --> 00:19:49,579
♪Will find its way to be fulfilled
one day♪

254
00:19:49,580 --> 00:19:56,179
♪But I want more
than just that fleeting gaze♪

255
00:19:56,180 --> 00:20:02,580
♪Still I have not heard your answer♪

256
00:20:02,980 --> 00:20:09,299
♪Can we still rewrite the ending
we face?♪

257
00:20:09,300 --> 00:20:14,420
♪When regrets begin to turn around you
will hear it all♪

258
00:20:14,900 --> 00:20:17,900
♪Everything that leads me back to you♪
